'''Al Hamriyah Sports Club''' is a [[association football|football]] club from [[Al Hamriyah]], Sharjah, United Arab Emirates. They play in the [[UAE Division One]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Al Hamriyah SC|url=https://int.soccerway.com/national/united-arab-emirates/division-1---group-a/20162017/regular-season/r35298/|publisher=Perform Group|accessdate=4 February 2017}}</ref>

==History==
Al Hamriyah joined the [[UAE Division One]] in the 2008/09 season.<ref>{{cite web|title=Masfut Season|url=https://int.soccerway.com/teams/united-arab-emirates/al-hamriyah/9972/matches/|publisher=Perform Group|accessdate=4 February 2017}}</ref>

