{{Infobox company | name = Arizona Soccer Association | type = Nonprofit youth sports organization | foundation = 1974 | location = Phoenix, Arizona, United States | industry = Youth sports (soccer) | products = Seasonal youth soccer programs | homepage = [http://www.azyouthsoccer.org Official web site] }}
{{Arizona-sport-stub}}
The '''Arizona Soccer Association''' (ASA), also known as the '''Arizona Youth Soccer Association''' (AYSA), is a nonprofit organization which was founded in 1974. The organization’s goals are to promote the physical, mental and emotional growth and development of the youth of Arizona through soccer.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.handsonphoenix.org/organization/001A000000sC9rzIAC |publisher=HandsOn Greater Phoenix |accessdate=10 June 2018 |title=Organization Profile: Arizona Youth Soccer Association}}</ref> The ASA/AYSA is a member of the [[United States Youth Soccer Association]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usyouthsoccer.org |publisher=[[United States Youth Soccer Association]] |accessdate=10 June 2018 |title=US Youth Soccer}}</ref> and the [[United States Soccer Federation]]. They are also associated with Phoenix Rising FC Youth Soccer Clubs,<ref>{{cite web |title=Forms and Documents |url=http://www.scottsdalesoccer.com/forms-and-documents |website=scottsdalesoccer.com |accessdate=10 June 2018}}</ref> which was formed when Scottsdale Soccer, the Blackhawks and the [[Phoenix Rising FC]] Charities merged in May 2018.<ref>{{cite news |title=Phoenix Rising FC Charities Join Forces With Scottsdale Soccer and the Blackhawks to Create Phoenix Rising FC Youth Soccer Clubs |url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/phoenix-rising-fc-charities-join-forces-with-scottsdale-soccer-and-the-blackhawks-to-create-phoenix-rising-fc-youth-soccer-clubs-300643653.html |accessdate=10 June 2018 |publisher=[[Phoenix Rising FC]] |date=7 May 2018}}</ref> The organization is partially supported by fund-raising events.<ref>{{cite news |title=McDonald’s hosting fundraising event for Arizona Youth Soccer Association |url=http://www.eastvalleytribune.com/local/gilbert/article_b1838a82-c9af-11e3-abd3-0019bb2963f4.html |accessdate=10 June 2018 |publisher=[[East Valley Tribune]] |date=30 April 2014}}</ref>
