{{Distinguish|Lirim Kastrati (footballer, born January 1999)}} {{Infobox football biography |name = Lirim Kastrati |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = Lirim Kastrati |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1999|2|2|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Mališevo]], [[Serbia and Montenegro|FR Yugoslavia]] |height = {{convert|1.65|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}} |position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] |currentclub = [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]] |clubnumber = 54 |youthyears1 = {{0|0000}}–2013 |youthclubs1 = [[Vigontina San Paolo F.C.#San Paolo Padova|San Paolo Padova]] |youthyears2 = 2013–2018 |youthclubs2 = [[A.S. Roma|Roma]] |youthyears3 = 2018– |youthclubs3 = [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]] |years1 = 2018– |clubs1 = [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]] |caps1 = 0 |goals1 = 0 |nationalyears1 = 2015–2016 |nationalteam1 = [[Albania national under-17 football team|Albania U17]] |nationalcaps1 = 3 |nationalgoals1 = 1<!--Only official matches are included.--> |nationalyears2 = 2018– |nationalteam2 = [[Kosovo national under-19 football team|Kosovo U19]] |nationalcaps2 = 1 |nationalgoals2 = 0 |nationalyears3 = 2017– |nationalteam3 = [[Kosovo national football team|Kosovo]] |nationalcaps3 = 2 |nationalgoals3 = 0 |club-update = 23 July 2018 |nationalteam-update = 21 March 2018 }} '''Lirim Kastrati''' (born 2 February 1999) is a [[Kosovo Albanian]] professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for Italian club [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]] and the [[Kosovo national football team|Kosovo national team]].
==Club career== ===Bologna=== On 23 July 2018. Kastrati signed his first professional contract with [[Serie A]] side [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]] after agreeing to a three-year deal.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/bologna/?action=read&idtmw=1137733|title=ESCLUSIVA TMW - Bologna, fatta per Kastrati. Accordo triennale|trans-title=EXCLUSIVE TMW - Bologna, fatta per Kastrati. Accordo triennale|language=Italian|website=TUTTOmercatoWEB.com|date=23 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/bologna/?action=read&idnet=Ym9sb2duYW5ld3MubmV0LTE1NTU3|title=Preso il kosovaro Kastrati: per il difensore contratto triennale|trans-title=Taken the Kosovan Kastrati: for the three-year contract defender|language=Italian|website=TUTTOmercatoWEB.com|date=23 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://futbollikosovar.com/zyrtare-lirim-kastrati-tranferohet-te-kjo-skuader-ne-serie-a-foto/20793/perfaqesuesja/|title=Zyrtare: Lirim Kastrati tranferohet te kjo skuadër në Serie A (Foto)|trans-title=Official: Lirim Kastrati transferred to this team in Serie A (Photo)|language=Albanian|website=Futbolli Kosovar|date=23 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://lajmi.net/zyrtare-lirim-kastrati-transferohet-te-bologna/|title=ZYRTARE: Lirim Kastrati transferohet te Bologna|trans-title=OFFICIAL: Lirim Kastrati transferred to Bologna|language=Albanian|website=Lajmi.net|date=23 July 2018}}</ref> Although signed contract with the first team, he continued to play for youth sector of Bologna.
