'''Lietuvos plaukimo federacija''' is the governing body of swimming in [[Lithuania]]. It is a non-profit organization that was founded in 1924. During the [[Soviet Union]] occupation, federation was closed and re-founded at 1991.<ref>[http://www.ltuswimming.com/joomla/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=48&Itemid=27&lang=lt ltuswimming.com]</ref> It is both a member of [[Ligue Européenne de Natation|LEN]] and [[FINA]].

