'''Monrovia Black Star Football Club''' is a club based in [[Monrovia]], [[Liberia]]. Its home stadium is the [[Antonette Tubman Stadium]]. In 2008, the club won the [[Liberian Premier League|Liberian Premier League (LPL)]] and [[Liberian Cup]] for the first time in its history.

