{{unreferenced|date=August 2012}}

'''Sports Coaching Foundation''', Hyderabad is a private [[cricket]] coaching [[academy]] run by Ex-[[Andhra_Pradesh_cricket_team|Andhra Ranji]] [[cricketer]] Sai Baba. The cricket academy is one of the first of its kind to introduce [[floodlight]]s and indoor nets in [[India]]; the power is supplied free by the electricity board of [[Andhra Pradesh]].

